text: Besarta Leci (born 14 October 1993) is a Kosovar footballer who plays as a goalkeeper and has appeared for the Kosovo women's national team. ==Career== Leci has been capped for the Kosovo national team, appearing for the team during the UEFA Women's Euro 2021 qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Kosovan women's footballers Category:Kosovo women's international footballers Category:Women's association football goalkeepers
